== plain argument lists both markers:
ZQdir_marker/
ZQmarker_file
== a quoted semicolon does not split the segment:
ZQdir_marker/
ZQmarker_file
== a quoted pipe does not split the segment:
ZQdir_marker/
ZQmarker_file
== a quoted ampersand does not split the segment:
ZQdir_marker/
ZQmarker_file
== a real separator still starts a new command segment:
ZQdir_marker/
ZQmarker_file
